title: Qal’at Salah El-Din/Fortress of Saladin
description: An ancient castle, located in modern Syria. Inscribed as a UNESCO World Heritage Site in 2006 as part of the "Crac des Chevaliers and Qal’at Salah El-Din" listing.

properties.description: Location of Qal’at Salah El-Din. Coordinates determined by eye in Google Earth in November 2012, following description in UNESCO World Heritage List.
